# Input

```svelte
{#await expression} <p></p> {:then name} <p></p> {:catch name} <p></p> {/await}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#await expression}
	<p></p>
{:then name}
	<p></p>
{:catch name}
	<p></p>
{/await}

```
